main event: A small very brilliant object dove vertically from a high altitude at tremendous speed near Philadelphia Airport.
interesting points: The object was observed from a distance of 2 miles northwest of the airport., The speed was estimated to be very high in relation to jet aircraft., The sighting was reported as a brief observation., There were two visual sightings from the ground by witnesses., The report concluded with insufficient information regarding the object's identity.
witness description: witnesses at addresses approximately 2 miles northwest of the airport
